  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905130/extras/1df0de11f15d8fadbb040b70a5a4f04e.poster.avif?t=1750100495\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905130/extras/1df0de11f15d8fadbb040b70a5a4f04e.webm?t=1750100495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905130/extras/1df0de11f15d8fadbb040b70a5a4f04e.mp4?t=1750100495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Doggo Dig Down</i> is a cozy, creative sandbox platformer where you play as a determined pup on a mission to bury a very important bone.<br><br>But digging down isn't so simple. You'll have to suck up blocks to clear a path, build into the sky, and discover power-ups along the way. New paint colors, hats, and even a jetpack await.<br><br>🐶 Want to race to the bottom of the world?<br><br>🧱 Prefer building massive pixel art in the clouds?<br><br>❄️ Or tackle \"Ice Mode\" for a true digging challenge?<br><br>It’s all up to you in this simple sandbox game made for good dogs.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905130/extras/1df0de11f15d8fadbb040b70a5a4f04e.poster.avif?t=1750100495\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905130/extras/1df0de11f15d8fadbb040b70a5a4f04e.webm?t=1750100495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905130/extras/1df0de11f15d8fadbb040b70a5a4f04e.mp4?t=1750100495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Doggo Dig Down</i> is a cozy, creative sandbox platformer where you play as a determined pup on a mission to bury a very important bone.<br><br>But digging down isn't so simple. You'll have to suck up blocks to clear a path, build into the sky, and discover power-ups along the way. New paint colors, hats, and even a jetpack await.<br><br>🐶 Want to race to the bottom of the world?<br><br>🧱 Prefer building massive pixel art in the clouds?<br><br>❄️ Or tackle \"Ice Mode\" for a true digging challenge?<br><br>It’s all up to you in this simple sandbox game made for good dogs.",
